des:
Home Kalley products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your light, outlet and air purifier.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your light, outlet and air purifier - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Home Kalley products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Home Kalley" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Home Kalley" app;
(3). You need to have some Home Kalley devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Home Kalley" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Home Kalley" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Home Kalley" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Home Kalley", and you'll be navigated to "Home Kalley" login page;
(9). Open "Home Kalley" App, click More Service, choose "Alexa". Link with Verification Code, copy the Code, put code into the login page
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn on the outlet.”
“Alexa, turn off the outlet.”
“Alexa, turn on the air purifier.”
“Alexa, turn off the air purifier.”
